<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
        }

        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .activation-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .user-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #777;
        }

        .social-media {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .social-media a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ranjitdasofficial/rdserver/main/Premium/1704973749103_im.png" alt="Your Company" class="logo">
            <h2>Payment Confirmation - Premium Membership Verification</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p> <strong> Dear <%= name %>,</strong></p>

            <p>We have successfully received your payment for the premium membership at KIIT CONNECT. Thank you for choosing
                our premium services! Your payment details are as follows:</p>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> <%= amount %> INR</li>
                <li><strong>Payment Date:</strong> <%= paymentDate %></li>
            </ul>

            <p>Your premium membership is currently under verification. Once the verification process is complete, your
                premium features will be activated, and you will receive another email with the activation details.</p>

            <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to contact our support team at 21053420@kiit.ac.in.</p>

            <p>Thank you for choosing KIIT CONNECT!</p>

            <div class="user-info">
                <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
                <p><strong>Branch:</strong> <%= branch %></p>
                <p><strong>Year:</strong> <%= year %></p>
                <p><strong>Payment Status:</strong> Verifying..</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>For further assistance, contact our support team at 21053420@kiit.ac.in</p>
            <div class="social-media">
                <a href="https://github.com/technicalranjitofficial/" target="_blank">Github</a>
                <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/C2RE26X5AMWDbswA7EbFVa" target="_blank">WhatsApp-1</a>
                <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/BAgHPirA4JzANjGKDd8z2q" target="_blank">WhatsApp-2</a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/kiitconnect/" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            <p>&copy; 2024 KIIT-CONNECT. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
